CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Wing Yip Food sells and markets its products under its flagship brand "Wing Yip" which can trace its history back to 1915, when its predecessor business began processing and selling cured sausages. We are one of the notable meat product processing companies in mainland China. Our products are primarily marketed and sold across 18 provinces in mainland China through 7 self-operated stores, 72 distributors, including major retail outlets and supermarkets and 7 e-commerce platforms, including one platform owned by us.
